WEBVTT

00:06.465 --> 00:08.259
- Hey.
- What's up?

00:10.053 --> 00:12.764
You got there scrambled eggs, huh?

00:12.847 --> 00:16.100
Well, they started off over easy and
then I started thinking about Dad.

00:16.184 --> 00:17.686
[banging]

00:21.230 --> 00:22.857
Told him about the job, did you?

00:23.775 --> 00:24.776
- What'd he say?
- [sighs]

00:25.359 --> 00:28.237
He said, and I quote...

00:33.827 --> 00:35.286
[chuckles] That's pretty bad.

00:35.369 --> 00:36.830
Hang on. I'm not done.

00:40.249 --> 00:41.375
Damn.

00:42.293 --> 00:44.128
I'm sure he didn't mean that last part.

00:45.964 --> 00:48.592
He spends years telling me I'm
not good enough to run a ranch,

00:48.675 --> 00:49.735
then somebody wants to give me a shot

00:49.759 --> 00:51.302
and all of a sudden I'm the asshole?

00:51.385 --> 00:52.679
Yeah, that's messed up.

00:52.762 --> 00:54.263
You've always been an asshole.

00:55.264 --> 00:56.474
Exactly.

00:56.558 --> 00:59.811
Dad calling me an asshole is
like pot calling the kettle...

00:59.894 --> 01:01.229
an asshole.

01:03.522 --> 01:04.941
- Hey, Dad.
- [sighs]

01:05.942 --> 01:07.193
Hey, morning, Dad.

01:07.276 --> 01:09.195
Hustle it up. We've got cows to feed.

01:09.278 --> 01:10.404
[Colt] Yep.

01:10.488 --> 01:12.240
You guys need help?

01:16.410 --> 01:19.581
Oh, Dad, stop before you don't
say something you're gonna regret.

01:21.124 --> 01:22.751
You don't work here anymore.

01:24.460 --> 01:27.505
Yeah, I know, but I got two
weeks 'til my new job starts,

01:27.588 --> 01:28.715
so I can still help.

01:28.798 --> 01:32.093
Why don't you use that time
to find someplace else to live?

01:33.136 --> 01:34.178
What?

01:36.681 --> 01:38.767
You don't work here,
you don't live here.

01:40.184 --> 01:41.435
Let's get going.

01:42.771 --> 01:45.564
Dad, uh... you can't just kick him out.

01:45.649 --> 01:47.441
Colt, you know what?
Don't worry about it.

01:47.525 --> 01:49.378
You don't want me here?
Fine. I'm leaving right now.

01:49.402 --> 01:50.482
Oh, come on, dude. Come on.

01:50.528 --> 01:52.656
Well, apparently, I'm
not welcome here anymore.

01:52.739 --> 01:54.240
What're you...

01:54.323 --> 01:56.492
No one's welcome here. So what?

01:58.953 --> 02:00.705
Good luck, man. You're gonna need it.

02:02.832 --> 02:03.958
What're you doing?

02:04.042 --> 02:05.919
You don't like it, you can go with him.

02:07.128 --> 02:09.380
Where're you go...
What is everyone doing?

02:09.463 --> 02:11.465
Why can't this just
be like every other day

02:11.549 --> 02:13.259
where we all just hate each other?

02:15.637 --> 02:16.680
Fuck!

02:16.763 --> 02:18.765
[theme music playing]

